dxf2svg.animation
Class ElementEvent

java.lang.Object
  dxf2svg.util.Attribute
      dxf2svg.animation.ElementEvent
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Cloneable
Deprecated. Removed in favour of the more flexible and general Attribute

public class ElementEvent
extends Attribute
implements java.lang.Cloneable

This class is the encapsulation of graphical element events. Graphical elements are things like lines, polylines, polygones, text, circles and the rest. All these elements can be made to 'listen' for events like onMouseDown and onClick.

Version:
0.1 - March 3, 2004
Author:
Andrew Nisbet
